race.comment: MANOLO BLING (6) showed a stack of pace and boxed on well under pressure to hold third in the Listed Goldmarket over 1100m at the Gold Coast last start. Excellent 1000m sprinter who carries 1kg less despite the drop in grade. Perfectly drawn so she has excellent credentials. POWER OF THE BRAVE (8) made it two wins on the trot when he came to Queensland last start and just got the prize in a BM78 over this distance at the Sunshine Coast. Acid test today but drops 6kgs and his record at this journey reads very well. TIGER TIE (7) has led from the outset to win two from two this prep, each time at today's distance. Will boot up and probably lead again from barrier one and despite the class rise he will give a ton of cheek. VODKA MARTINI (3) ran on well behind TIGER TIE last time. Raced well in stakes grade here three back so do not rule him out.
